<h1>Appointments</h1><br/>
<p>Please note that if you are booking any mani/pedi combo service with two nail techs at the same time, you should call in to book. If you book a manicure and pedicure together on the website, your service will be scheduled for two hours.  Additionally, If you are booking services for two people at the same time, it is best to create log-ins for both people and book each individual separately. If you book two appointments under one log-in name, it will book the appointments an hour apart.</p>
